<promed@promedmail.org>
[Some cases may well be pneumonic plague, but it would seem extremely
unlikely that the large outbreak involving more than 1300 individuals is
due to _Y. pestis_ pneumonia, primary or secondary, unless the strain is
much less virulent than usual. - Mod.LL]
